39
00:03:20.163 --> 00:03:22.115
Himmel, cool.

40
00:03:22.165 --> 00:03:23.283
Dobbeltbogstaver...

41
00:03:23.333 --> 00:03:25.243
Hertuginde Carrie
kan lide dobbeltbogstaver.


42
